Title: The Game Plan
Writer: Dan Fogelman (created by), Joe Lawson, Aurin Squire (story editor), Kay Oyegun (staff writer)
Actors: Milo Ventimiglia, Mandy Moore, Sterling K. Brown, Chrissy Metz
Plot: Jack and Rebecca disagree about the future, Toby makes a gesture to Kate which backfires, Beth surprises Randall, while Kevin and William have a heart-to-heart.
